# CODEOWNERS

## Default Owners
* @project-lead

## Package Ownership

### Core
packages/core/ @arch
packages/core/**/*.ts @arch

### Renderer
packages/renderer/ @renderer
packages/renderer/**/*.ts @renderer

### 2D Animations
packages/animations-2d/ @anim2d
packages/animations-2d/**/*.ts @anim2d

### 3D Animations
packages/animations-3d/ @anim3d
packages/animations-3d/**/*.ts @anim3d

### AI Intake
packages/intake/ @intake
packages/intake/**/*.ts @intake

### Assets
packages/assets/ @assets
packages/assets/**/*.ts @assets

## Application Ownership

### Studio App
apps/studio/ @dev
apps/studio/**/*.tsx @dev
apps/studio/**/*.ts @dev

## Documentation & Configuration

### Documentation
docs/ @docs
docs/**/*.md @docs

### DevOps & CI/CD
.github/ @devops
.github/**/* @devops

### Testing
tests/ @testing
tests/**/* @testing

## Review Requirements

- All PRs require at least 1 reviewer
- Breaking changes require 2 reviewers
- Changes to core contracts require approval from @arch
- Changes to renderer require approval from @renderer
- Changes to 3D animations require approval from @anim3d
- Changes to CI/CD require approval from @devops
